  dialogueLines:
  - 'Well you have done quite excellently Duncan, '
  - i suppose destroying those walking corpses would have been difficult for one
    like you
  - 'If only you had been in time to find your son, what a shame '
  - I can however offer you a way to find and save your son
  - You have proven resourceful perhaps you could prove so again
  - 'If you will take my offer walk into the portal. If not .... you may stay here
    until you rethink your postion '
  - I have made it quite impossible for you to leave if you had not noticed
  - Take my offer Duncan you have greater creatues of the Shadow to fight before
    you will save your son
  - 'Though I wonder what you will do Duncan when you find out what your child did '
  - hahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahaha
